This paper focuses on the practical aspects of deep learning development and deployment, including the comparison of different frameworks and platforms, prediction accuracy, and performance. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper also discusses software bugs and compatibility issues, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
